snippet.title: Chapter One: Run for eat (Trailer)
snippet.description:
Eat more burger than you can!
run for eat is the new the laba 's game , where you have to run and collect burgers.
Drive the  guy and throw the burgers to find out which of the three wall can be destroyed.

Collects all the run animations  and increadible funny accessories.

Share your result and become the king of the  guys!
